  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.28,
    "endTime": 403.6,
    "text": "library sits by your back door"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.6,
    "endTime": 405.039,
    "text": "for a couple of weeks longer than it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.039,
    "endTime": 406.72,
    "text": "should"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.72,
    "endTime": 409.919,
    "text": "you lose a cd you spill your coffee on a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.919,
    "endTime": 411.199,
    "text": "book"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.199,
    "endTime": 412.96,
    "text": "suddenly we're not here for you so much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.96,
    "endTime": 415.039,
    "text": "anymore because if that happens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 415.039,
    "endTime": 417.52,
    "text": "we're going to make you pay for it and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.52,
    "endTime": 419.44,
    "text": "if you can't pay for it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.44,
    "endTime": 422.24,
    "text": "you're out of luck i have been a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.24,
    "endTime": 424.08,
    "text": "librarian for a lot of years and in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.08,
    "endTime": 426.0,
    "text": "past few years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.0,
    "endTime": 429.039,
    "text": "i myself have paid over 500 in league"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.039,
    "endTime": 431.36,
    "text": "fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.36,
    "endTime": 433.039,
    "text": "now you might wonder why i mean i'm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.039,
    "endTime": 434.72,
    "text": "there every day and i certainly know how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.72,
    "endTime": 436.72,
    "text": "the system works"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.72,
    "endTime": 438.72,
    "text": "but like all of our friends at the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.72,
    "endTime": 440.319,
    "text": "library"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.319,
    "endTime": 443.44,
    "text": "i am busy i lose track of things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.44,
    "endTime": 446.639,
    "text": "my house is sometimes messy and i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.639,
    "endTime": 451.199,
    "text": "have lost a dvd or two under the sofa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.199,
    "endTime": 453.919,
    "text": "and i have been fortunate enough to be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.919,
    "endTime": 455.199,
    "text": "able to pay"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.199,
    "endTime": 458.24,
    "text": "that 500 over the last several years if"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.24,
    "endTime": 459.599,
    "text": "not happily"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.599,
    "endTime": 462.319,
    "text": "at least had the means to do it so is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.319,
    "endTime": 464.56,
    "text": "that fair and equitable service"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.56,
    "endTime": 468.0,
    "text": "if some of us can pay our fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.0,
    "endTime": 469.52,
    "text": "and continue to operate as we always"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.52,
    "endTime": 471.599,
    "text": "have and others of us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.599,
    "endTime": 473.759,
    "text": "make one mistake and no longer are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 473.759,
    "endTime": 476.16,
    "text": "welcome back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.16,
    "endTime": 479.84,
    "text": "it's simply not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.16,
    "endTime": 482.879,
    "text": "now why would we continue to operate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.879,
    "endTime": 484.879,
    "text": "under a model that hurts"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.879,
    "endTime": 487.52,
    "text": "our most vulnerable patrons the most"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.52,
    "endTime": 489.28,
    "text": "there are reasons"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.28,
    "endTime": 491.28,
    "text": "there are reasons like responsibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.28,
    "endTime": 492.639,
    "text": "there are some libraries that really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.639,
    "endTime": 494.56,
    "text": "feel that it's our job to teach people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.56,
    "endTime": 496.08,
    "text": "responsibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.08,
    "endTime": 497.28,
    "text": "and they haven't figured out that there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.28,
    "endTime": 498.8,
    "text": "might be ways to do that that don't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.8,
    "endTime": 501.52,
    "text": "equate to dollars"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.52,
    "endTime": 503.52,
    "text": "there's also this idea that we share the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.52,
    "endTime": 505.44,
    "text": "resources collectively in a community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.44,
    "endTime": 507.36,
    "text": "and so we have to take turns"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.36,
    "endTime": 509.84,
    "text": "if i keep my my little pony movie for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.84,
    "endTime": 510.72,
    "text": "too long"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.72,
    "endTime": 512.24,
    "text": "and somebody else wants to watch it it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.24,
    "endTime": 514.32,
    "text": "not fair"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514.32,
    "endTime": 516.56,
    "text": "and then there's the money community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.56,
    "endTime": 517.36,
    "text": "members"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.36,
    "endTime": 518.959,
    "text": "often love their libraries and they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.959,
    "endTime": 520.399,
    "text": "don't want us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.399,
    "endTime": 522.159,
    "text": "to not be able to sustain the services"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.159,
    "endTime": 524.64,
    "text": "we offer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.8,
    "endTime": 526.399,
    "text": "luckily we can address all of these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.399,
    "endTime": 528.08,
    "text": "things in a variety of ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.08,
    "endTime": 529.92,
    "text": "without scaring away our most vulnerable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.92,
    "endTime": 532.24,
    "text": "populations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.24,
    "endTime": 534.64,
    "text": "some libraries have gone to a netflix"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.64,
    "endTime": 535.6,
    "text": "model"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.6,
    "endTime": 537.2,
    "text": "you might be familiar with this you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.2,
    "endTime": 538.64,
    "text": "check things out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.64,
    "endTime": 540.08,
    "text": "when you're done with them you return"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.08,
    "endTime": 541.68,
    "text": "them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.68,
    "endTime": 543.36,
    "text": "if you don't return them you can't check"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.36,
    "endTime": 544.88,
    "text": "more things out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.88,
    "endTime": 547.36,
    "text": "but once you do it's all forgiven it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.36,
    "endTime": 548.88,
    "text": "fine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.88,
    "endTime": 551.92,
    "text": "you can check out again others continue"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.92,
    "endTime": 553.36,
    "text": "to charge fines but they want to offer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.36,
    "endTime": 554.88,
    "text": "alternatives to their library"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.88,
    "endTime": 556.959,
    "text": "patrons and so they do things like food"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.959,
    "endTime": 558.399,
    "text": "for fines where you bring in canned"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 558.399,
    "endTime": 559.2,
    "text": "goods"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.2,
    "endTime": 560.72,
    "text": "or read away your fines where you can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.72,
    "endTime": 562.32,
    "text": "read off your fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.32,
    "endTime": 563.519,
    "text": "there's even another library in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.519,
    "endTime": 564.959,
    "text": "wisconsin that offers scratch-off"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.959,
    "endTime": 566.399,
    "text": "tickets at their counter so you can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.399,
    "endTime": 567.839,
    "text": "scratch off and get 10"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 567.839,
    "endTime": 570.88,
    "text": "off or 20 off your fines that day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.88,
    "endTime": 573.44,
    "text": "and there are amnesty days one day a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.44,
    "endTime": 575.68,
    "text": "year you bring back your late materials"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575.68,
    "endTime": 579.279,
    "text": "and all is forgiven there was a library"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.279,
    "endTime": 581.12,
    "text": "in san francisco that did an amnesty day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.12,
    "endTime": 582.24,
    "text": "last year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.24,
    "endTime": 584.08,
    "text": "and they welcomed back five thousand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584.08,
    "endTime": 586.48,
    "text": "users who had been blocked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.48,
    "endTime": 588.32,
    "text": "that same day they received more than"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588.32,
    "endTime": 589.68,
    "text": "seven hundred"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.68,
    "endTime": 593.2,
    "text": "items that were overdue among them was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.2,
    "endTime": 596.32,
    "text": "one book that was 100 years overdue"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.32,
    "endTime": 599.2,
    "text": "so i know that sounds ridiculous but i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.2,
    "endTime": 601.36,
    "text": "experienced that people will stay away"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.36,
    "endTime": 603.2,
    "text": "from the library rather than face the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.2,
    "endTime": 604.72,
    "text": "authority of the librarian when they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.72,
    "endTime": 606.48,
    "text": "have late items"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.48,
    "endTime": 608.079,
    "text": "as michael might have mentioned i've"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.079,
    "endTime": 610.399,
    "text": "been a librarian for 15 years and my mom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.399,
    "endTime": 612.56,
    "text": "hasn't been in a library in decades"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 612.56,
    "endTime": 616.16,
    "text": "because when she was young she lost a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.839,
    "endTime": 618.0,
    "text": "book"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.0,
    "endTime": 621.12,
    "text": "so these are great baby steps but they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.12,
    "endTime": 621.839,
    "text": "don't go"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.839,
    "endTime": 625.519,
    "text": "far enough because"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.519,
    "endTime": 628.16,
    "text": "they make people jump through hoops they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.16,
    "endTime": 629.6,
    "text": "have to come on the right days at the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 629.6,
    "endTime": 630.48,
    "text": "right times"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.48,
    "endTime": 632.56,
    "text": "they might have to have extra food to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.56,
    "endTime": 633.68,
    "text": "share"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633.68,
    "endTime": 635.04,
    "text": "they want to read away their fines they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.04,
    "endTime": 637.759,
    "text": "need to be literate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637.839,
    "endTime": 639.92,
    "text": "if we want people to use the library"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.92,
    "endTime": 641.76,
    "text": "again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.76,
    "endTime": 644.839,
    "text": "we should just get rid of fines all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.839,
    "endTime": 646.16,
    "text": "together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.16,
    "endTime": 647.68,
    "text": "now you might think i've forgotten a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.68,
    "endTime": 649.279,
    "text": "money piece where"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 649.279,
    "endTime": 652.24,
    "text": "we need to finance libraries right but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.24,
    "endTime": 653.76,
    "text": "there's a couple of things to consider"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653.76,
    "endTime": 654.959,
    "text": "when we think about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.959,
    "endTime": 659.36,
    "text": "how fines function in library budgets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.36,
    "endTime": 662.24,
    "text": "the first is that fines have never been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.24,
    "endTime": 663.519,
    "text": "a stable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663.519,
    "endTime": 664.88,
    "text": "source of revenue they've always"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.88,
    "endTime": 667.279,
    "text": "fluctuated and in fact they've continued"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.279,
    "endTime": 668.64,
    "text": "to go down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668.64,
    "endTime": 671.839,
    "text": "over the last few decades when the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.839,
    "endTime": 673.519,
    "text": "recession hit especially people's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.519,
    "endTime": 675.839,
    "text": "ability to pay was hit as well"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.839,
    "endTime": 678.079,
    "text": "so for a lot of those 10 000 friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678.079,
    "endTime": 679.2,
    "text": "that we've got at the library that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 679.2,
    "endTime": 680.72,
    "text": "aren't able to use it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.72,
    "endTime": 682.88,
    "text": "they might never be able to pay us when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.88,
    "endTime": 684.399,
    "text": "we talk about eliminating their fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 684.399,
    "endTime": 685.839,
    "text": "we're not losing money"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.839,
    "endTime": 689.839,
    "text": "so much as the idea of money"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 689.839,
    "endTime": 692.8,
    "text": "and thirdly you might be surprised to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692.8,
    "endTime": 693.68,
    "text": "know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.68,
    "endTime": 695.68,
    "text": "fines on average nationally are about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 695.68,
    "endTime": 697.04,
    "text": "one and a half percent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.04,
    "endTime": 699.68,
    "text": "of a library's operating budget now that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 699.68,
    "endTime": 700.959,
    "text": "can still be a lot of money if you're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 700.959,
    "endTime": 702.64,
    "text": "looking at a large library or a large"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702.64,
    "endTime": 703.92,
    "text": "library system"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.92,
    "endTime": 706.48,
    "text": "the dollar amount can be high but it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706.48,
    "endTime": 707.839,
    "text": "an achievable cut"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.839,
    "endTime": 711.279,
    "text": "for most libraries to absorb and finally"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.279,
    "endTime": 713.68,
    "text": "and maybe most importantly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713.68,
    "endTime": 716.72,
    "text": "fines cost us money to collect when you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.72,
    "endTime": 718.0,
    "text": "start to factor in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.0,
    "endTime": 720.0,
    "text": "all of the ways that we collect fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720.0,
    "endTime": 722.56,
    "text": "supplies like mailers that we send out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 722.56,
    "endTime": 725.839,
    "text": "to remind people of their fines services"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.839,
    "endTime": 729.2,
    "text": "like collections management services"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 729.2,
    "endTime": 731.12,
    "text": "even telephone and email notifications"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 731.12,
    "endTime": 733.2,
    "text": "can cost libraries money"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 733.2,
    "endTime": 736.56,
    "text": "and staff time is a huge cost for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 736.56,
    "endTime": 737.68,
    "text": "libraries"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.68,
    "endTime": 739.519,
    "text": "so that our frontline staff is standing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 739.519,
    "endTime": 740.959,
    "text": "there talking to people about their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740.959,
    "endTime": 741.519,
    "text": "fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 741.519,
    "endTime": 743.04,
    "text": "sometimes arguing with people about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 743.04,
    "endTime": 745.04,
    "text": "fines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 745.04,
    "endTime": 747.92,
    "text": "when we eliminate all of those pieces if"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 747.92,
    "endTime": 749.76,
    "text": "we got rid of fines we might actually"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749.76,
    "endTime": 751.44,
    "text": "save money in our libraries"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 751.44,
    "endTime": 753.76,
    "text": "or at the very least we would be able to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 753.76,
    "endTime": 755.68,
    "text": "reallocate our staff time to pursuits"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 755.68,
    "endTime": 757.2,
    "text": "that better fit those missions we talked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 757.2,
    "endTime": 759.839,
    "text": "about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 760.24,
    "endTime": 761.76,
    "text": "the other thing i want everybody to come"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 761.76,
    "endTime": 763.6,
    "text": "away understanding is that fines don't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 763.6,
    "endTime": 765.12,
    "text": "actually work to do what we think they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.12,
    "endTime": 766.32,
    "text": "do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 766.32,
    "endTime": 768.24,
    "text": "the debate about fines whether we should"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 768.24,
    "endTime": 770.16,
    "text": "find how much we should find it isn't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 770.16,
    "endTime": 770.8,
    "text": "new"
